                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="16751104" author="graemerocher1" created="Thu, 24 Jan 2019 13:08:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Causing &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/issues/1103&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/issues/1103&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16752181" author="paulk" created="Fri, 25 Jan 2019 11:37:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I presume that code in &lt;tt&gt;TraitComposer&lt;/tt&gt; was written before we added support for the &lt;tt&gt;parameters&lt;/tt&gt; switch. The test suite still passes and behavior seems to be expected with pre-compiled code when we simply just copy the parameter name. We probably just need to have a suitable workaround (or error) if a parameter has name &lt;tt&gt;$self&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16753302" author="paulk" created="Sun, 27 Jan 2019 06:12:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Should be fixed now.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
